\/","url_meta":{"origin":26334,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Shade: Allah shades those who give relief","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever grants respite to someone in difficulty or relieves him, Allah will shade him on the Day of Resurrection when there is no shade but His.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1306 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28991,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/09\/allah-expose-riya-shirk-asghar\/","url_meta":{"origin":26334,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hypocrisy: Allah will expose hypocrites on Judgment Day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Jundub reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever acts to be heard, Allah will make him heard. Whoever acts to show off, Allah will show him off. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6499, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2987 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9675,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/02\/health-food-faith-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":26334,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Life: Whoever is healthy, safe, faithful has everything","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubaydullah ibn Mihsan reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever among you wakes up secure in his property, healthy in his body, and he has his food for the day, it is as if he were given the entire world.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2346\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26334","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=26334"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26334\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=26334"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=26334"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=26334"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}